{"tid":2193743,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"連登兒子丹麥浚龍Juno 新歌《我在切爾諾貝爾 等你》討論區","createTime":"2020-09-08T05:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T18:41:40.000Z","uid":57328,"like":17,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0968d1b5916e67ac7f01dccfa172001cf04fc448","tid":2193743,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/1HgQaAlzNoB8b25gPcxmF2?si=Q86fcqtMQzSruL1xCqykTQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Falbum%2F1HgQaAlzNoB8b25gPcxmF2%3Fsi%3DQ86fcqtMQzSruL1xCqykTQ&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=97621e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/album/1HgQaAlzNoB8b25gPcxmF2?si=Q86fcqtMQzSruL1xCqykTQ</a><br />\n<br />\n作詞：黃偉文    作曲：Bert<br />\n編曲：黃兆銘 (Chaser arranged by Eric Chan)<br />\n監製：麥浚龍 / Bert<br />\n<br />\n等～你<br />\n在這崩潰的課室<br />\n沙礫裡<br />\n埋住了未染污之靈<br />\n<br />\n等～你<br />\n在這傾側的教堂<br />\n這命危巨塔<br />\n乃最初跟最後那約定<br />\n<br />\n何解心暗喜<br />\n在這焦黑的戲院<br />\n堅貞到<br />\n陪著偉大建築殉情<br />\n<br />\n如必需炸毁<br />\n留在世上那點幅射<br />\n都將會<br />\n叫世間 想起我的璀璨<br />\n<br />\n如若有天 這城又見 白灰飛 鋪千里<br />\n旁人在四竄 我們留在這地<br />\n存亡若有命 洪爐熔掉 不必刻意避<br />\n情願抱著你 同享這毒氣 誰又希罕有生機<br />\n<br />\n等～你<br />\n在這長草的議會<br />\n不需要<br />\n庸人在決定 我的將來<br />\n<br />\n如必需炸毁<br />\n留在世上那點幅射<br />\n都將會<br />\n成明天 苦戀者～信仰<br />\n<br />\n如若有天 這城又見 白灰飛 鋪千里<br />\n旁人在四竄 亦都不走等～你<br />\n存亡若有命 洪爐熔掉 不必刻意避<br />\n情願抱著你 完成這壓軸戲<br />\n同遺落 放射塵 滿地<br />\n<br />\n如爆炸計時開始了<br />\n繼續愛 也是某種傳～奇<br />\n才能教會世人<br />\n學識 不捨不棄<br />\n<br />\n世界雖說大<br />\n前行和後退 也沒慈悲<br />\n<br />\n情願抱著你 Ha～<br />\n完成這壓軸戲 腳踏這地<br />\n同享這毒氣 也許守出個生機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如若有天￼￼，我在 切爾諾貝爾 等你<br />\n<br />\n一別，此處￼<br />\n<br />\nthank you and enjoy. <br />\n<br />\n￼<a href=\"http://www.chapelofdawn.com/junomak-single-ngo-joi-chit-yi-nok-bui-yi-dang-nei/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chapelofdawn.com%2Fjunomak-single-ngo-joi-chit-yi-nok-bui-yi-dang-nei%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=1f1e1f46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chapelofdawn.com/junomak-single-ngo-joi-chit-yi-nok-bui-yi-dang-nei/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/645425758932983/posts/1918373264971553/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F645425758932983%2Fposts%2F1918373264971553%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=bc3079b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/645425758932983/posts/1918373264971553/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"04b6ccd9c9562d00f5cf2c29b559d96ae1089444","tid":2193743,"uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nUNWYJk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnUNWYJk.jpg&h=0db6deac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a6cf253ebab13638d9e6cf76e773706c383369e","tid":2193743,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"冇魔鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bfbe7cf3edbbfd0ced441615d919c8ac6f4eb0","tid":2193743,"uid":17799,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死藍絲"},{"pid":"cd071997a6b230c7e18282451c28226d8fd70c05","tid":2193743,"uid":244361,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"比佢唱真係浪費晒"},{"pid":"a1921ee448e5fdd4f300642591213d3f61396dc7","tid":2193743,"uid":197782,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"真係好聽喎.."},{"pid":"a8d6775133720c03b8256f4ad6e7d336a564ef90","tid":2193743,"uid":833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:47:46.000Z","msg":"仲未睇hbo 果套切爾諾貝爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a9138f3389e1193dcfab71dcc95df6a3c620a3","tid":2193743,"uid":90601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"副歌tune\b+和音夾到勁重味精 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果俾其他女聲cover應該另一個世界"},{"pid":"f6fb7d78f57d42b56aa37a7f87946db129489f1e","tid":2193743,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"Juno好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd62679aee5e1d1b02b31830d629d5cfc4980ae","tid":2193743,"uid":82268,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"係咪終於最後一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4272a22d377f16e9755f01572b5a39515301d9d3","tid":2193743,"uid":32442,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"有d悶同mk 好似比姜濤唱都ok咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ed7fa009a9e3fd53f45c1777c7a45497cda7ff","tid":2193743,"uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"🥰《Channel新歌速遞》董浦戀揭最終章😎Juno新歌帶大家進入核災難現場😱😱<br />\n<br />\n「董浦」戀有結局了！😊踏入最終章，董折竟為情出走，闖入核災難現場！Juno麥浚龍新歌《我在切爾諾貝爾 等你》今天派台，成為故事結局篇的引子。由Juno與Kay謝安琪合演的「董折與浦銘心」愛情故事歷時三年，隨著一首首作品訴說著兩個角色不同年代的心路歷程， Juno選擇以切爾諾貝爾這個地方作為結局篇的場景，原來是三年來的精心鋪排！🤓<br />\n<br />\nJuno率先分享：「這個地方是故事的起源，三年的企劃也應該在這個地方完結。切爾諾貝爾這個地方經歷一夜突變，沒有圓滿下場，象徵人生的荒誕與失落。」追溯《勇悍・17》歌詞最後兩句「約定未來要到切爾諾貝爾跟你闖闖，當然心跳冒汗&hellip;」，就會發現董折決心要到切爾諾貝爾，其實是角色有感每天勞碌活着，然後因為一件事情，決心在有生之年要到訪這個地方。<br />\n<br />\n想不到是，《我在切爾諾貝爾 等你》用上較甜蜜曲式，以鋼琴及小提琴作編曲主軸，但尾段曲風突然轉換，以長達分半鐘的純音樂作結。Juno解釋這正正是董折的心態：「《我在切爾諾貝爾 等你》唱完後，我希望表達角色心態上的突然轉變，那是一段較叛逆、無奈的畫外情感，與故事情節息息相關。其實人生不只容納感情，還有種種無可奈何和身不由己。」為配合歌曲主題，《我在切爾諾貝爾 等你》的唱片封面和照片都設定Juno身在切爾諾貝爾核電廠災難附近的城鎮普里皮亞芝（Pripyat），站在標誌性的摩天輪前留影；加上猶如廢墟的場景設計，就像Juno親身前往當地拍攝一樣。<br />\n<br />\nJuno還透露，原來13年前他已對切爾諾貝爾情有獨鍾：「一直喜歡這地方，亦喜歡相關故事和影集，甚至在《the album part one》出現前，已覺得這是一片『可惜』的地方。之前拍攝電影《風林火山》也想到前往當地取景，可惜當時因為輻射問題，加上逗留時間、拍攝人數及安全性等不同方面的考慮，始終未能償願。近年聽說好了點，但暫時還未有前往的打算。慶幸近年多了有關這地方的電影、劇集，讓人多了解這個地方。」 時空轉移，真心不變，大家是否很期待新歌MV？<br />\n<br />\n編輯：安迪<br />\n<br />\n===================<br />\nHONG KONG SINGER CHANNEL<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hksingerchannel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksingerchannel.com&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=2c66fe31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hksingerchannel.com</a><br />\nHong Kong Singer Channel<br />\nIG: hkscchannel<br />\n<br />\n#hongkongsingerchannel #hkscchannel #hksingerchannel #hongkongsinger #我在切爾諾貝爾等你 #麥浚龍 #董折 #浦銘心 #切爾諾貝爾情 Juno Mak 麥浚龍 麥浚龍國際歌迷會"},{"pid":"a988b1903002ce0922011246d6c8cecad544f6f7","tid":2193743,"uid":185565,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"呢個系列肯完未啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a6f1d4ef9bbd81853befbb96572fe5e8147b16","tid":2193743,"uid":31323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cdd62679aee5e1d1b02b31830d629d5cfc4980ae","tid":2193743,"uid":82268,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"係咪終於最後一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"未有耐完啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />